      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"Worth monitoring all of these in the market with a field of eight newcomers going to post. 8. MRS MALIBU is a filly by Mertadam out of Ronaycan. Set to debut for the Abdullah Atas stable where a bold showing is expected providing her first start on the track. 1. ERGIDEN is a three-year-old colt by Ayabakan out of Belenkiz also representing the Abdullah Atas yard. Serious contender first time up. 4. KINDBERO is a three-year-old colt by Kislali out of Kizil Goz on opening start for the Seyit Gokce team. Keep safe. 3. HIRCIN DADAS is a colt on first outing from the stable of Haci Kurt. By Deha from Polen.\",\"runners\":[8,1,4,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
